      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The photograph features a mobile cinema screening. The cinema equipment and operator are positioned on a platform. The standing audience – mainly consisting of men in hats and jackets – is turned towards the screen. The operator is looking towards the camera.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The inscription below the photograph notes that this was the first mobile cinema in Serbia to screen a film in a village in the Šumadija region.</ab>
